snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio only belongs to Rohail Hyatt. None can match his style of production. Every song produced by him strucks you so hard (if you listen) that it takes you away from this world. The tunes of every instrument is so catchy (idk it's the natural frequencies he mentioned in an interview but walla e alam). Sadly we are so influenced by Bolly/Holly music that we are forgetting our roots. For me, his music has changed something inside of me for good. Thank you so much Rohail Hyatt♥️.May people understand what you're trying to convey!
snippet.textOriginal: Coke Studio only belongs to Rohail Hyatt. None can match his style of production. Every song produced by him strucks you so hard (if you listen) that it takes you away from this world. The tunes of every instrument is so catchy (idk it's the natural frequencies he mentioned in an interview but walla e alam). Sadly we are so influenced by Bolly/Holly music that we are forgetting our roots. For me, his music has changed something inside of me for good. Thank you so much Rohail Hyatt♥️.May people understand what you're trying to convey!
